Have you looked at the Famicom Game Repeater by Hori?  It looks pretty cool.  The trick to it seems to be that it uses a controlled pass-through for the system power.  If timed right, theoretically that should allow random number generators to be seeded in a repeatable way.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=10">Memblers</a> — Wed Dec 02, 2009 12:42 pm</p><hr />
